  "title": "CENTRE PRINCIPAL",
  "description": "<p>Job Description & Requirements</p><p>Preschool is looking for a passionate and motivated Principal to lead and support our growing team. We welcome fresh graduates who are eager to start their leadership journey in early childhood education.</p><p><u><strong>Job Description:</strong></u></p><p>Oversee daily centre operations</p><p>Lead and guide teachers</p><p>Ensure curriculum quality and smooth classroom management</p><p>Maintain strong communication with parents</p><p>Uphold centre standards, safety, and compliance</p><p><u><strong>Requirements:</strong></u></p><p>Diploma / Degree in Early Childhood Education (L2 certified preferred)</p><p>Strong passion for working with children</p><p>Good communication and leadership skills</p><p>Fresh graduates are encouraged to apply — training will be provided<br /></p><p>Working location: Jubilee Road (West Coast)</p><p>Why Join Us?</p><p>Supportive working environment</p><p>Opportunities for professional growth</p><p>Friendly team and positive culture</p>",
